name: JSON / Generated README
body:
### May 2016

This version of `open-source-ios-apps` has its data in [`JSON` format](https://github.com/dkhamsing/open-source-ios-apps/pull/273) (thanks to @scribblemaniac). Updating `contents.json` will trigger a README conversion that is pushed back to GitHub through CI.

name: Manual
body:
### May 2016

This is the last version of the `open-source-ios-apps` README that was updated manually.
- Over 300 apps
- [80 contributors](https://github.com/dkhamsing/open-source-ios-apps/graphs/contributors)
